subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Mark Wiebe followed his opening 66 with a 65 to take a three-stroke lead in the Outback Steakhouse Pro-Am, the Champions Tour event in Lutz, Fla. Wiebe reached 11 under to tie the event 36-hole record.
